title: PM felicitates Pakistan Vollyball team on winning Central Asia Championship
content:
ISLAMABAD, May 17 (APP): Prime Minster Shehbaz Sharif on Friday felicitated the Pakistan Vollyball team on winning the Central Asia Championship.
“Talent and teamwork at its best. Pakistan won all its six matches during the tournament,” he said in his post on X.
“Congratulations to Team Pakistan,” he added.
